phrases: That is fine with me, but does not your country provide them for you?
You are from the mainland, are not you?
Or is it something you cannot tell your lady?
I am not going to ask a bunch of rude questions!
I do not want you getting angry.
I, Qin, will do my best for the love between you two!
It would be best to ambush them.
I will say it once more.
I am just giving a suggestion since your plan has a high chance of failure.
Nothing will come out of fighting!
So what are you saying we should do?
Spread a rumor that you are going to sell me.
Our enemies will jump at the chance.
Do you understand what you are suggesting?
Do you think I do not?
You are wary of those who attacked me in Okinawa.
We cannot run away from them, though.
There is a doll watching me.
Because I have not called out to it yet.
Spread a rumor that a doll will be on sale.
This girl is not a doll!
Dolls are supposed to have stone cold expressions!
You do not see this kind of quality often!
It is completely different from a normal doll!
Its observation spirit takes on a human form, you see!
He is even telling them that it has an observation specter with a human form.
It is true that it would be hard to reel in buyers in this area with a normal doll.
Should we just take this chance?
We will see how things play out for a little while longer.
Anyway, I do not think you should be here.
I have no attachment to this body, but I think I will consider your suggestion.
Why did you keep quiet about the enemy's doll?
If you were worried this whole time, why did not you tell me?
I do not know where to go either.
Why are you saying that now?
You do not remember what you just said?
You can tell me anything next time.
I want to be with you forever, just like this.
I got caught by a dangerous gang!
I knew bad people would get involved,
but these guys are too much!
I do not think we should go.
We should run while we can!
There is no turning back if we go on!
They do not usually deal in dolls.
Because I am interested in them.
I heard she had a human-shaped observation specter, so I was wondering what kind of girl she would be.
She looks like your average doll though.
I did not think we would be meeting here, my lady!
I thought we were supposed to meet at Lo's store?
I would not mind buying it.
Go ahead and look for yourself.
I will not let them lay a hand on you.
I should not have gotten involved...
Let us see if she is the real thing or not.
If you were not told to say that, then that means you are not a doll.
No matter what terrible things dolls are forced to suffer,
they would never speak out of line in deference to their owner.
I can see that you are basing your assumptions on a typical doll.
I cannot tell what I am anymore when I am with this man.
Whether I am a doll or not, I had no intention of dealing with you.
You were planning to kill us anyway.
I will try to keep her quiet, so I am really sorry!
And how will you dodge them this time?
This has to be a joke!
I just felt there was something different about you...
Do not do anything hasty now.
If she is the real thing, then your strength has proven it...
I received some information from a special guest
that there was a woman with a human-shaped specter and her protector, a male contractor.
The contractor is supposed to have great physical abilities and can manipulate electricity.
You have the ability to stand on even terms with me,
and that is exactly what proves you are the Black Reaper.
If I had known it would turn out like this, I would have prepared better for my remuneration.
If I strengthen my ability just a bit more, you will be completely crushed.
I will give you some time.
You can no longer win against-
There is no point in fighting back.
You should tell her yourself, as well.
She is no longer human, anyway.
Tell her to come quickly to my side.
Anyway, let us get out of here!
Not like I can stay in Hong Kong anymore.
I will use this money to escape.
That doll seems to be the real Izanami.
Still, it would be such a waste to kill it.
So we will be parting ways, Madame Oreille.
